title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 153: Featuring Henrik Lundqvist + Mike Commodore
description:
On Tuesday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets, the guys are joined by arguably the best-looking person on the planet, Henrik Lundqvist. The Rangers goalie stops by the West Coast Wagon Tour to discuss how his season has been going, to talk about some of his teammates, his career, his clothes and a ton more. Hank also gives some legendary stories, just as you'd expect. The guys then follow up with an interview with the insiderrr himself, Mike Commodore. Commie joins to talk trade deadline and more. The guys also go division by division and discuss all the big trades in the NHL after Monday's trade deadline.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
